{
  "message": "test(harness): add golden snapshot baselines for editor tests\n\nAdd insta snapshot files for all editor_snapshots.rs test cases:\n- Cursor positioning: start, middle, end\n- Selection states: word, word_boundary, multiline, all\n- Text operations: insert, delete, newline, undo, redo, multi_undo\n- Multi-line: basic, cursor on line 2, vertical scroll\n- Edge cases: empty, placeholder, narrow viewport, line numbers\n- Unicode: basic, emoji, combining chars, RTL\n\nThese serve as regression baselines for the Advanced Text Editor widget.\nRun BLESS=1 cargo test to update after intentional changes.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
